---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ExternalLink from "../components/ExternalLink.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Gary Ritchie.">
  <main id="main" class="prose">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      I've been playing with computers since the early 1980s, starting with a TRS-80 Color Computer
      with 4K of RAM where I taught myself to program in BASIC and 6809 assembly language.
    </p>
    <p>
      My first paid software job was in 1989, and I've been working as a developer ever since, with
      an almost 20-year stint at Microsoft, a brief time at Apple, and almost 10 years at Posit
      (formerly RStudio), where I am still working.
    </p>
    <p>More to come...</p>
    <p>
      If you want to reach me, <a href="mailto:kitty.dwell3q@icloud.com">email works</a>. I'm also
      on <ExternalLink href="https://github.com/gtritchie" rel="me">GitHub</ExternalLink>.
    </p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: var(--reading-width);
  }
  .prose p {
    margin: var(--sp-4) 0;
  }
</style>
